        "title": "feat(mistral): add Monthly Plan menu bar metric (subscription usage)",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nCloses #1363.\n\n- add a Mistral Monthly Plan menu bar metric backed by the console Vibe usage endpoint\n- keep Pay-as-you-go API spend available and preserve existing extra usage windows\n- send only the validated CSRF cookie/token to `console.mistral.ai`; keep admin Ory session cookies origin-bound\n- bound the optional console request to the existing billing deadline with a 4-second cap\n- validate percentage bounds, clamp stored settings, localize picker labels, and document the provider behavior\n\n## Live proof\n\n- issue #1363 contains the contributor's redacted successful request and response for the exact endpoint: only `csrftoken` plus `X-CSRFToken`, returning `usage_percentage` and `reset_at`\n- contributor verified the settings picker, persisted selection, Monthly Plan percentage/reset display, Pay-as-you-go fallback, and no-plan fallback against a real account\n- screenshots below show the provider setting and rendered result\n\n## Verification\n\n- `swift test --filter 'MistralUsageParserTests|MistralVibeUsageTests|MenuBarMetricWindowResolverTests|SettingsStoreAdditionalTests|ProvidersPaneCoverageTests'` - 71 tests passed\n- `make check` - passed; localization parity, SwiftFormat, and SwiftLint clean\n- whole-branch Codex autoreview clean with endpoint evidence supplied, confidence 0.86\n\nExact candidate: `ff58880f`.\n\n<img width=\"384\" height=\"449\" alt=\"Mistral Monthly Plan metric setting\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/f371509a-6942-4a7c-b34d-9f0bc3c2df3b\" />\n<img width=\"904\" height=\"862\" alt=\"Mistral Monthly Plan usage result\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c4c6c2bf-3d93-489d-addd-d79ba0dce536\" />\n",
